videos.headline: Texas WR Smith absorbs huge hit on TD from Ehlinger
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger zips a short pass to Jake Smith, who breaks the plane before getting cracked by a TCU defender to complete the 5-yard Texas touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas WR Smith absorbs huge hit on TD from Ehlinger) 2020/10/3 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eagles soars to end zone for long Texas TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger hits Brennan Eagles in stride for a 45-yard Texas score, Ehlinger's second touchdown strike of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Eagles soars to end zone for long Texas TD) 2020/10/3 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson makes defenders dance on Texas' 4th-down TD
videos.description: Roschon Johnson catches a pass from Sam Ehlinger and makes a move toward the goal line on fourth down to cash in a Texas touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Johnson makes defenders dance on Texas' 4th-down TD) 2020/10/3 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger tosses 4 TDs in Texas' first loss of season
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger throws for over 200 yards passing and four touchdowns, but the Longhorns fall to unranked TCU 33-31.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ehlinger tosses 4 TDs in Texas' first loss of season) 2020/10/3 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: TCU hands No. 9 Texas first loss in heartbreaking fashion
videos.description: TCU overcomes a four-touchdown performance by Sam Ehlinger with a 33-31 road victory against No. 9 Texas.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (TCU hands No. 9 Texas first loss in heartbreaking fashion) 2020/10/3 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Texas coughs up backbreaking fumble at 1-yard line
videos.description: Texas' opportunity to take a late-fourth- quarter lead over TCU is wiped away as Keaontay Ingram fumbles at the Horned Frogs' 1-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas coughs up backbreaking fumble at 1-yard line) 2020/10/3 ESHEET
